        "timestamp": "2019-07-17 17:22:48.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4: Code-Review-1\n\nJust a suggestion:\nWe have two cases here.\n\nCase1. Automated tests\nCase2. Deployment of just CDS component.\n\nFor the second case, we would not have message router, hence adding a dependency on it won't start CDS.\n\nI think we should introduce some global variable, which will be true by default (but disabled during stand-alone CDS deployment)\n\nAnd the dependency added to the init container should be wrapped in that var, as well as the properties added to application.conf (which will be looked up by annotation ConditionalOnProperty to enable some bean you're using for testing..)",
        "patchset_number": 4
      },
